data.text:
Orlando's rainy season has finally returned!
Sorry tourists but it will rain EVERY afternoon and we need it!
Other people in America get excited about winter or fall.
Orlando gets excited about rain.
Anything to cool off what feels like walking on the surface of the sun every day
